Chia-Jui Chen, Peter C. Hoch, Peter H. Raven. 1992. Systematics of Epilobium (Onagraceae) in China. Volumen 34 de Systematic botany monographs. Ed. Am. Soc. of Plant Taxonomists. 209 pp. ISBN 0912861347
